review: I went to see the doctor because I was having all signs of pregnancy, but negative Urine test. She recommended me to wait for one week and get Thyroid tested. I was having dizziness and pains, for which I was asked to meet a general physician.I was not at all satisfied with the diagnosis, so I met another doctor, **** ***** **** *** ********** *** *** ** **** **** ******* ********** ** * **** ****** *** *** **** **** * *** ***** ** **** ***** **** **** ** ***** Very disappointed, will never recommend.
reply_text: I am surprised and sorry to know that it turned out to be an ectopic pregnancy. I also explained to you about the option of getting a blood test done and repeating it after 48 hours. But you were in a hurry about getting back to work. Moreover you told me that your urine pregnancy test was negative on the morning you came to visit me. We often see patients running around anxiously with no diagnosis on ultrasound or blood tests with morbid fear of ectopic pregnancy. I preferred to have a more conservative approach. It is unfortunate that you feel that your life was put at risk. Anyways glad that your condition is diagnosed. All the best
